{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"As a child,"},{"time":3000,"text":"I was raised by native Hawaiian elders --"},{"time":6000,"text":"three old women"},{"time":8000,"text":"who took care of me while my parents worked."},{"time":12000,"text":"The year is 1963."},{"time":15000,"text":"We're at the ocean."},{"time":17000,"text":"It's twilight."},{"time":19000,"text":"We're watching the rising of the stars"},{"time":23000,"text":"and the shifting of the tides."},{"time":26000,"text":"It's a stretch of beach we know so well."},{"time":30000,"text":"The smooth stones on the sand"},{"time":33000,"text":"are familiar to us."},{"time":37000,"text":"If you saw these women on the street"},{"time":39000,"text":"in their faded clothes,"},{"time":41000,"text":"you might dismiss them"},{"time":43000,"text":"as poor and simple."},{"time":45000,"text":"That would be a mistake."},{"time":48000,"text":"These women are descendants"},{"time":50000,"text":"of Polynesian navigators,"},{"time":52000,"text":"trained in the old ways"},{"time":55000,"text":"by their elders,"},{"time":57000,"text":"and now they're passing it on to me."},{"time":60000,"text":"They teach me the names of the winds and the rains,"},{"time":64000,"text":"of astronomy according to a genealogy of stars."},{"time":68000,"text":"There's a new moon on the horizon."},{"time":71000,"text":"Hawaiians say it's a good night for fishing."},{"time":74000,"text":"They begin to chant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77000,"text":"[Hawaiian chant]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":107000,"text":"When they finish,"},{"time":109000,"text":"they sit in a circle"},{"time":111000,"text":"and ask me to come to join them."},{"time":114000,"text":"They want to teach me about my destiny."},{"time":118000,"text":"I thought every seven-year-old went through this."},{"time":120000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":124000,"text":"\"Baby girl,"},{"time":126000,"text":"someday the world will be in trouble."},{"time":129000,"text":"People will forget their wisdom."},{"time":132000,"text":"It will take elders' voices"},{"time":135000,"text":"from the far corners of the world"},{"time":138000,"text":"to call the world into balance."},{"time":142000,"text":"You will go far away."},{"time":144000,"text":"It will sometimes be a lonely road."},{"time":147000,"text":"We will not be there."},{"time":149000,"text":"But you will look into the eyes"},{"time":151000,"text":"of seeming strangers,"},{"time":154000,"text":"and you will recognize your ohana,"},{"time":157000,"text":"your family."},{"time":159000,"text":"And it will take all of you."},{"time":162000,"text":"It will take all of you.\""},{"time":166000,"text":"These words, I hold onto"},{"time":169000,"text":"all my life."},{"time":171000,"text":"Because the idea of doing it alone"},{"time":174000,"text":"terrifies me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"The year is 2007."},{"time":180000,"text":"I'm on a remote island in Micronesia."},{"time":183000,"text":"Satawal is one half-mile long"},{"time":186000,"text":"by one mile wide."},{"time":189000,"text":"It's the home of my mentor."},{"time":191000,"text":"His name is Pius Mau Piailug."},{"time":193000,"text":"Mau is a palu,"},{"time":195000,"text":"a navigator priest."},{"time":197000,"text":"He's also considered"},{"time":199000,"text":"the greatest wave finder in the world."},{"time":202000,"text":"There are fewer than a handful"},{"time":204000,"text":"of palu left on this island."},{"time":207000,"text":"Their tradition is so extraordinary"},{"time":210000,"text":"that these mariners sailed"},{"time":212000,"text":"three million square miles across the Pacific"},{"time":215000,"text":"without the use of instruments."},{"time":218000,"text":"They could synthesize patterns in nature"},{"time":221000,"text":"using the rising and setting of stars,"},{"time":224000,"text":"the sequence and direction of waves,"},{"time":227000,"text":"the flight patterns of certain birds."},{"time":230000,"text":"Even the slightest hint of color"},{"time":233000,"text":"on the underbelly of a cloud"},{"time":235000,"text":"would inform them"},{"time":237000,"text":"and help them navigate with the keenest accuracy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"When Western scientists would join Mau on the canoe"},{"time":246000,"text":"and watch him go into the hull,"},{"time":248000,"text":"it appeared that an old man"},{"time":250000,"text":"was going to rest."},{"time":252000,"text":"In fact, the hull of the canoe"},{"time":254000,"text":"is the womb of the vessel."},{"time":256000,"text":"It is the most accurate place"},{"time":259000,"text":"to feel the rhythm and sequence"},{"time":262000,"text":"and direction of waves."},{"time":264000,"text":"Mau was, in fact,"},{"time":266000,"text":"gathering explicit data"},{"time":268000,"text":"using his entire body."},{"time":271000,"text":"It's what he had been trained to do"},{"time":273000,"text":"since he was five years old."},{"time":276000,"text":"Now science may dismiss this methodology,"},{"time":280000,"text":"but Polynesian navigators use it today"},{"time":284000,"text":"because it provides them"},{"time":287000,"text":"an accurate determination"},{"time":289000,"text":"of the angle and direction"},{"time":291000,"text":"of their vessel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293000,"text":"The palu also had"},{"time":295000,"text":"an uncanny ability"},{"time":297000,"text":"to forecast weather conditions"},{"time":299000,"text":"days in advance."},{"time":301000,"text":"Sometimes I'd be with Mau on a cloud-covered night"},{"time":304000,"text":"and we'd sit at the easternmost coast of the island,"},{"time":307000,"text":"and he would look out,"},{"time":310000,"text":"and then he would say,"},{"time":312000,"text":"\"Okay, we go.\""},{"time":314000,"text":"He saw that first glint of light --"},{"time":316000,"text":"he knew what the weather was going to be three days from now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"Their achievements, intellectually and scientifically,"},{"time":323000,"text":"are extraordinary,"},{"time":325000,"text":"and they are so relevant"},{"time":327000,"text":"for these times that we are in"},{"time":329000,"text":"when we are riding out storms."},{"time":333000,"text":"We are in such a critical moment"},{"time":336000,"text":"of our collective history."},{"time":341000,"text":"They have been compared"},{"time":343000,"text":"to astronauts --"},{"time":345000,"text":"these elder navigators"},{"time":347000,"text":"who sail vast open oceans"},{"time":350000,"text":"in double-hulled canoes"},{"time":353000,"text":"thousands of miles"},{"time":355000,"text":"from a small island."},{"time":358000,"text":"Their canoes, our rockets;"},{"time":361000,"text":"their sea, our space."},{"time":365000,"text":"The wisdom of these elders"},{"time":367000,"text":"is not a mere collection"},{"time":369000,"text":"of stories about old people"},{"time":372000,"text":"in some remote spot."},{"time":374000,"text":"This is part of our collective narrative."},{"time":377000,"text":"It's humanity's DNA."},{"time":380000,"text":"We cannot afford to lose it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383000,"text":"The year is 2010."},{"time":387000,"text":"Just as the women in Hawaii"},{"time":390000,"text":"that raised me predicted,"},{"time":392000,"text":"the world is in trouble."},{"time":396000,"text":"We live in a society"},{"time":399000,"text":"bloated with data,"},{"time":401000,"text":"yet starved for wisdom."},{"time":405000,"text":"We're connected 24/7,"},{"time":409000,"text":"yet anxiety,"},{"time":411000,"text":"fear, depression and loneliness"},{"time":414000,"text":"is at an all-time high."},{"time":416000,"text":"We must course-correct."},{"time":420000,"text":"An African shaman said,"},{"time":423000,"text":"\"Your society worships the jester"},{"time":426000,"text":"while the king stands"},{"time":428000,"text":"in plain clothes.\""},{"time":435000,"text":"The link between the past and the future"},{"time":438000,"text":"is fragile."},{"time":440000,"text":"This I know intimately,"},{"time":442000,"text":"because even as I travel"},{"time":445000,"text":"throughout the world"},{"time":447000,"text":"to listen to these stories and record them,"},{"time":451000,"text":"I struggle."},{"time":458000,"text":"I am haunted"},{"time":461000,"text":"by the fact that I no longer remember"},{"time":465000,"text":"the names of the winds and the rains."}]},{"cues":[{"time":474000,"text":"Mau passed away"},{"time":477000,"text":"five months ago,"},{"time":479000,"text":"but his legacy and lessons live on."},{"time":483000,"text":"And I am reminded"},{"time":487000,"text":"that throughout the world"},{"time":490000,"text":"there are cultures"},{"time":492000,"text":"with vast sums of knowledge in them,"},{"time":496000,"text":"as potent as the Micronesian navigators,"},{"time":500000,"text":"that are going dismissed,"},{"time":502000,"text":"that this is a testament"},{"time":504000,"text":"to brilliant, brilliant"},{"time":506000,"text":"technology and science and wisdom"},{"time":509000,"text":"that is vanishing rapidly."},{"time":511000,"text":"Because when an elder dies a library is burned,"},{"time":514000,"text":"and throughout the world, libraries are ablaze."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518000,"text":"I am grateful for the fact"},{"time":521000,"text":"that I had a mentor like Mau"},{"time":524000,"text":"who taught me how to navigate."},{"time":527000,"text":"And I realize"},{"time":529000,"text":"through a lesson that he shared"},{"time":532000,"text":"that we continue to find our way."},{"time":534000,"text":"And this is what he said:"},{"time":537000,"text":"\"The island is the canoe;"},{"time":539000,"text":"the canoe, the island.\""},{"time":542000,"text":"And what he meant was,"},{"time":545000,"text":"if you are voyaging"},{"time":547000,"text":"and far from home,"},{"time":549000,"text":"your very survival depends"},{"time":551000,"text":"on everyone aboard."},{"time":554000,"text":"You cannot make the voyage alone,"},{"time":557000,"text":"you were never meant to."},{"time":559000,"text":"This whole notion of every man for himself"},{"time":561000,"text":"is completely unsustainable."},{"time":563000,"text":"It always was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566000,"text":"So in closing I would offer you this:"},{"time":570000,"text":"The planet is our canoe,"},{"time":574000,"text":"and we are the voyagers."},{"time":577000,"text":"True navigation"},{"time":579000,"text":"begins in the human heart."},{"time":582000,"text":"It's the most important map of all."},{"time":585000,"text":"Together, may we journey well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}